  "_doc": "Manually-walked trailer prices for entries the static def parser sees as price=0 (and overrides for parser-incomplete entries). See AlexOQ/trucker#254. POLICY: prices reflect MINIMUM-money-to-outfit configuration — cheapest paintjob (min of paintjob_range) for budget/optimizer-friendly representation, not dealer-stock-default which bundles mid/premium paint. Decomposed via in-game customization screen.",
