    "paint": "minimum (cheapest paintjob in dealer's range, typically 2.6k single / 5.2k double / 7.8k HCT)",
    "rationale": "Optimizer's primary use case is min-cost garage outfitting. Stock-offer prices include cosmetic paint that the budget-conscious player would skip. Manual-prices.json represents the floor a player must pay for a working trailer.",
    "consequence": "Override deltas vs parser-derived prices reflect parser-missed accessory chains (chassis, body, base), NOT the cosmetic-paint addition."
  },
